parameters:
Announcer of the Underground Arena: 'A challenger has
appeared to challenge the absolute champion! Please welcome
these beautiful maidens with a big round of applause!'

Underground Arena Announcer: 'These are skilled fighters
who emerged victorious in the Pizuma Arena. They won't be as
pathetic as the challengers from the other day!'
Thief Nora: W-What happened to being pathetic...?

Priestess Sophia: Nora-chan's nose, you can understand it,
right? Even I can smell the scent of the large amount of
blood that flowed.

Thief Nora: Eeek...!? As I thought... What should we do...
I'm getting scared...

Mage Relm: No matter how strong the opponent is, there's
only one of them! I don't know about this absolute champion
or whatever, but I don't feel like losing!
Clea: Please watch. I'm coming out.

Underground Arena Announcer: The one who called is the Iron
Mask! No one knows their true face, but everyone knows they
are the strongest!

Underground Arena Announcer: Because of you, the bets won't
be settled! It's the entrance of the absolute champion of
the Underground Arena, the Iron Mask!

Underground Arena Announcer: We will have a match with a
special rule of 4 against 1. Can these maidens really defeat
the absolute champion!?
Underground Arena Announcer: And now, the match begins!
Guard Drone: Everyone, this way! Please move away!

Underground arena announcer: 'The absolute champion of the
underground arena! Once again, maidens have gathered to stop
the relentless advance of the Iron Mask!'

Underground arena announcer: 'No one has ever dared to
challenge him twice before! Overcoming fear and despair,
these maidens have returned!'

Underground arena announcer: 'The beautiful five maidens...
Will the legend of the Iron Mask end today, or will it
continue?'

Underground arena announcer: Make us witnesses to the
legend! Show us the sight of the Iron Mask falling!
Underground arena announcer: And now, the match begins!

Underground arena announcer: T-The winner is the
challenger! The undefeated champion, Iron Mask, has finally,
finally, finally been defeated!

Underground arena announcer: The legend has been shattered!
They are the chosen ones blessed by the goddess Actina!

Underground arena announcer: Now, it's time for some fun!
The fate of the underground arena is in the hands of the
victors!
Audience: Kill him! Kill him! Kill him! Kill him!

Underground arena announcer: The audience is calling for
his death! They are hoping to see the head of the former
absolute champion severed!

Underground arena announcer: Now, show us! Decapitate him
and create a new legend!
Clea: I won't kill him. I'll take him back with me.

Audience: Don't mess around! We won't leave until we see
blood!
Clea: I see... In that case, please come down here.

Clea: I can still fight. Is there anyone who wants to
challenge me, the one who defeated the absolute champion?

Clea: If there's no one here, then I'll go back. Well
then.

Announcer of the Underground Arena: The absolute champion
of the Underground Arena! The maiden who stopped the iron-
masked rapid advance has appeared once again!

Underground Arena Announcer: Will they be able to survive
in this merciless underground arena!?

Underground Arena Announcer: The maiden's rapid advance is
unstoppable, it was a magnificent battle!

Underground Arena Announcer: This will be the prize for the
winner.
Clea: Ugh... in a place like this...!

Underground Arena Announcer: The female participant has
been defeated! Her fate now rests in the hands of the
audience!

Underground Arena Announcer: Now, the curtain rises on a
show where lives are at stake!
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
Mage Relm: Ugh... Why is a genius like me...

Underground Arena Announcer: The female participant has
been defeated! Her fate now rests in the hands of the
audience!

Underground Arena Announcer: Now, please look forward to a
pitiful plea for life!
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
Thief Nora: Ow... it hurts... please stop...

Underground Arena Announcer: The female participant has
been defeated! Her fate now rests in the hands of the
audience!

Underground Arena Announcer: Now, please look forward to a
pitiful plea for life!
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
Priestess Sophia: Ugh... to be defeated like this...

Underground Arena Announcer: The female participant has
been defeated! Her fate now rests in the hands of the
audience!

Underground Arena Announcer: Now, the show begins with
